1. Važne su nam informacije koje smo dobili juče. (*važne*) (The information we received yesterday is important to us.)
2. Ova tema je vrlo važna za našu zemlju. (*važna*) (This topic is very important for our country.)
3. Kada pišete eseje, važno je da strukturišete vaše argumente. (*važno*) (When writing essays, it is important to structure your arguments.)
4. Oni su važni članovi našeg tima. (*važni*) (They are important members of our team.)
5. Važnije je da uspeš u onome što radiš, nego da budeš popularan. (*važnije*) (It is more important to succeed in what you do than to be popular.)
6. Važnost obrazovanja se često ne uzima ozbiljno. (*važnost*) (The importance of education is often not taken seriously.)
7. Ukoliko ne obratite pažnju na ove *važne* detalje, može doći do problema. (important) (If you don't pay attention to these important details, there may be problems.)
8. Moj posao zahteva da donosim *važne* odluke svakog dana. (important) (My job requires me to make important decisions every day.)
9. Tvoj savet mi je bio veoma *važan* u procesu donošenja odluke. (important) (Your advice was very important to me in the decision-making process.)
10. Kako bi se smanjila šteta, važno je da hitno preduzmete određene mere. (*važno*) (To reduce the damage, it is important that you take urgent measures.)